An Architectural Product Supplier & Installer
SGH helps architects & commercial builders from material selection & design through construction & owner move-in.
Learn More
 










 

 




  


Our Business Products
Our employees have an intricate knowledge of how the products perform and the best way to install them, which gives our staff the unique expertise you desire. We collaborate with owners, architect, and contractors to ensure that products look stunning from concept to completion.


 



Our Business Services
SGH goes beyond merely supplying architectural products. We know you need more than that to make your next building project a success. That’s why we’ve always provided a broad range of services to support you and your project team throughout the design and construction of your building.


 



Our Business Brand Integration
Your customers’ first impression of your business starts before they even walk through your front door. A connection begins when they first see your building. That’s why it’s so important your building makes an impact at every turn.


 



Our Business Blast Technology
Does your next commercial building project or facility upgrade require a higher level of security? Incorporating blast-resistant technology into your building to protect the lives and safety of the people and resources inside your buildings.


 
 
 







