Territory
SGH provides and installs a variety of exterior and interior architectural products to help make your commercial building project a success. 
We serve customers throughout the Midwest and Rockies.


SGH is centrally located in six offices throughout the Midwest and Rockies serving 10 states. But we do not stop there. Working closely with our associated companies, we have completed jobs in many cities throughout the United States.
