About SGH

For over 65 years, we’ve been helping you:
Create strong, safe, functional exteriors and interiors
Achieve successful commercial construction and renovation projects
Bring your architectural ideas to life
From the initial idea to the final details, we have the resources to successfully execute projects of any whatever size you have to tackle.
How to ensure your next building project succeeds
Beyond supplying architectural products, SGH provides expert installation services.
Our employees have an intricate knowledge of each product’s performance and the best ways to install them – giving our staff the professional insight you’ will want on your next project. We collaborate with you – building owners, architects and general contractors – to ensure the products look stunning from concept to completion.

 



 







